parameters:
\N<Hakase-kun>Ah, Boku-kun, welcome. You've come to play,
right? So, what do you want to do?

\N<Hakase-kun>Ah, Boku-kun, welcome. You've come to play,
right? Here, this is it. It's the promised mechanical
rhinoceros beetle.
\N<Boku>Wow! Thank you, Hakase-kun! I'll treasure it!
\N<Hakase-kun>Alright. So, what do you want to do?
\N<Boku>Hmm? How about playing hide and seek?

\N<Hakase-kun>Hide and seek, huh... It's cramped inside, so
how about we play a treasure hunt instead?

\N<Hakase-kun>I'll hide this capsule inside the house and
you, Boku-kun, will search for it. If you can find it within
100 seconds, you win.

\N<Hakase-kun>Alright then, let's do it. I'll go hide, so
wait for me.

\N<Hakase-kun>Sounds good. Alright then, let's do it. I'll
go hide, so wait for me.

\N<Hakase-kun>I hid it on the first floor. Alright, let's
start!

\N<Hakase-kun>I hid it on the first floor. Please go find
it.
